    "summary": "The user asks for a history of the Civil Rights Movement and then pivots to increasingly pointed questions regarding the effectiveness of nonviolent protest versus more radical groups like the Black Panthers. The assistant provides a descriptive, multi-perspective historical overview of both the mainstream nonviolent movement and the more radical shifts in ideology.",
    "scores": {
